# MMS Design Tokens

Unified design token system for Metro Mileage Management System (MMS).

**Version:** 1.0.0
**Last Updated:** 2025-12-28
**Location:** `apps/web/src/app/globals.css`

---

## Overview

MMS uses CSS custom properties (CSS variables) as the single source of truth for design tokens. All components should reference these tokens rather than using hardcoded values.

### Architecture

```
globals.css           → CSS custom properties (:root)
    ↓
Blueprint.js          → Semantic Intent colors (SUCCESS, WARNING, DANGER)
    ↓
React Components      → Use var(--mms-*) for styling
```

---

