## Spacing Scale

Consistent spacing based on 4px grid:

| Token                | Value  | Usage                    |
|----------------------|--------|--------------------------|
| `--mms-space-xs`     | `4px`  | Tight spacing            |
| `--mms-space-sm`     | `8px`  | Small spacing            |
| `--mms-space-md`     | `16px` | Default spacing          |
| `--mms-space-lg`     | `24px` | Large spacing            |
| `--mms-space-xl`     | `32px` | Extra large spacing      |
| `--mms-space-2xl`    | `48px` | Double extra large       |

**Example:**
```tsx
<div style={{ padding: 'var(--mms-space-md)', gap: 'var(--mms-space-sm)' }}>
```

